<L>__{interior crematorium day}
<A>__{carter, doreen, eddie and keith are in the front pews facing the catafalque on which frank's coffin rests. the vicar is already midway through the solemn words of the 'committal' when a woman enters. the clunk of her high heels cuts through the silence. everybody looks round.}
<C>__{carter}
<P>__{(whispering to doreen)}
<D>__{is that margaret?}
